5308 item_category_id calc_category( const itype &obj )
5309 {
5310  if( obj.gun && !obj.gunmod ) {
5311  return item_category_guns;
5312  }
5313  if( obj.magazine ) {
5314  return item_category_magazines;
5315  }
5316  if( obj.ammo ) {
5317  return item_category_ammo;
5318  }
5319  if( obj.tool ) {
5320  return item_category_tools;
5321  }
5322  if( obj.armor ) {
5323  return item_category_clothing;
5324  }
5325  if( obj.comestible ) {
5326  return obj.comestible->comesttype == "MED" ?
5327  item_category_drugs : item_category_food;
5328  }
5329  if( obj.book ) {
5330  return item_category_books;
5331  }
5332  if( obj.gunmod ) {
5333  return item_category_mods;
5334  }
5335  if( obj.bionic ) {
5336  return item_category_bionics;
5337  }
5338 
5339  bool weap = std::any_of( obj.melee.begin(), obj.melee.end(),
5340  []( const std::pair<const damage_type_id, float> &qty ) {
5341  return qty.second > MELEE_STAT;
5342  } );
5343 
5344  return weap ? item_category_weapons : item_category_other;
5345 }

5356 void item_group::debug_spawn()
5357 {
5358  std::vector<item_group_id> groups = item_controller->get_all_group_names();
5359  uilist menu;
5360  menu.text = _( "Test which group?" );
5361  for( size_t i = 0; i < groups.size(); i++ ) {
5362  menu.entries.emplace_back( static_cast<int>( i ), true, -2, groups[i].str() );
5363  }
5364  while( true ) {
5365  menu.query();
5366  const int index = menu.ret;
5367  if( index >= static_cast<int>( groups.size() ) || index < 0 ) {
5368  break;
5369  }
5370  // Spawn items from the group 100 times
5371  std::map<std::string, int> itemnames;
5372  for( size_t a = 0; a < 100; a++ ) {
5373  const ItemList items = items_from( groups[index], calendar::turn );
5374  for( const item &it : items ) {
5375  itemnames[it.display_name()]++;
5376  }
5377  }
5378  // Invert the map to get sorting!
5379  std::multimap<int, std::string> itemnames2;
5380  for( const auto &e : itemnames ) {
5381  itemnames2.insert( std::pair<int, std::string>( e.second, e.first ) );
5382  }
5383  uilist menu2;
5384  menu2.text = _( "Result of 100 spawns:" );
5385  for( const auto &e : itemnames2 ) {
5386  menu2.entries.emplace_back( static_cast<int>( menu2.entries.size() ), true, -2,
5387  string_format( _( "%d x %s" ), e.first, e.second ) );
5388  }
5389  menu2.query();
5390  }
5391 }

5393 bool Item_factory::has_template( const itype_id &id ) const
5394 {
5395  return m_templates.count( id ) || m_runtimes.count( id );
5396 }

5398 std::vector<const itype *> Item_factory::all() const
5399 {
5400  cata_assert( frozen );
5401 
5402  std::vector<const itype *> res;
5403  res.reserve( m_templates.size() + m_runtimes.size() );
5404 
5405  for( const auto &e : m_templates ) {
5406  res.push_back( &e.second );
5407  }
5408  for( const auto &e : m_runtimes ) {
5409  res.push_back( e.second.get() );
5410  }
5411 
5412  return res;
5413 }
5414 
5415 std::vector<const itype *> Item_factory::get_runtime_types() const
5416 {
5417  std::vector<const itype *> res;
5418  res.reserve( m_runtimes.size() );
5419  for( const auto &e : m_runtimes ) {
5420  res.push_back( e.second.get() );
5421  }
5422 
5423  return res;
5424 }

5426 /** Find all templates matching the UnaryPredicate function */
5427 std::vector<const itype *> Item_factory::find( const std::function<bool( const itype & )> &func )
5428 {
5429  std::vector<const itype *> res;
5430 
5431  std::vector<const itype *> opts = item_controller->all();
5432 
5433  std::copy_if( opts.begin(), opts.end(), std::back_inserter( res ),
5434  [&func]( const itype * e ) {
5435  return func( *e );
5436  } );
5437 
5438  return res;
5439 }
5440 
5441 std::list<itype_id> Item_factory::subtype_replacement( const itype_id &base ) const
5442 {
5443  std::list<itype_id> ret;
5444  ret.push_back( base );
5445  const auto replacements = tool_subtypes.find( base );
5446  if( replacements != tool_subtypes.end() ) {
5447  ret.insert( ret.end(), replacements->second.begin(), replacements->second.end() );
5448  }
5449 
5450  return ret;
5451 }
